name: Eggy The Pet Egg
description: $Eggy is the cutest and most charming pet egg you’ll ever meet, featuring the most adorable googly eyes on the Solana blockchain. This delightful companion is always by your side, radiating smiles and spreading joy throughout your day. Whether you’re looking for a touch of whimsy or a constant source of happiness, $Eggy is here to brighten your life and make every moment more enjoyable. Supported by Happy Bazinga!
